getInstructionProperty

public InstructionProperty getInstructionProperty(int index)
Returns the InstructionProperty with the given index from the Properties file. Unlike with arrays or Lists the index is one-based!

Parameters:
index - the index of the requested InstructionProperty
Returns:
the InstructionProperty
Throws:
IllegalArgumentException - if index is less than one or greater than the maximum allowed value
